
================================================================================
Version 0.1.0
================================================================================

General
- First official version
- Zlib/libpng license

Dependencies
- LUX Project 0.5.0

Features
- Single-line takeover using "require 'ufo'"
- New ufo.core.Engine class manages execution flow
- New ufo.core.Queue class implements a classic circular fixed-size queue
- New ufo.core.Activity class is extended to control game dynamics
- New ufo.core.Event class represents events sent to activities
- New ufo.core.Task class represents something an activity does for many frames
- New ufo.gui module with a dozen unstable and poorly defined GUI classes
